# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# MyFinPro — Production Environment Variable Schema
# This template shows ALL required variables for the production environment.
# Values are injected from GitHub Secrets at deploy time — no persistent .env on the server.
#
# ⚠️  SECURITY: All secrets are managed in GitHub Secrets and injected ephemerally.
#     The .env file is written at deploy time and shredded immediately after docker compose up.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── MySQL Database ──
# MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD  — Root password for MySQL (generate: openssl rand -base64 48)
# MYSQL_DATABASE       — Database name (e.g., myfinpro)
# MYSQL_USER           — Database user (e.g., myfinpro_prod)
# MYSQL_PASSWORD       — Database user password (generate: openssl rand -base64 48)

# ── Database Connection ──
# DATABASE_URL         — Full connection string: mysql://USER:PASS@mysql:3306/DB_NAME

# ── Authentication ──
# JWT_SECRET           — Secret for signing JWT access tokens (generate: openssl rand -base64 48)
# JWT_REFRESH_SECRET   — Secret for signing JWT refresh tokens (generate: openssl rand -base64 48)

# ── Redis ──
# REDIS_URL            — Redis connection string (e.g., redis://redis:6379)

# ── Application Config ──
# NODE_ENV             — Environment: production
# API_PORT             — API server port: 3001
# CORS_ORIGIN          — Allowed CORS origins (e.g., https://myfinpro.example.com)
# LOG_LEVEL            — Logging level: warn
# SWAGGER_ENABLED      — Enable Swagger docs: false (disabled in production)
# RATE_LIMIT_TTL       — Rate limit window in ms: 60000
# RATE_LIMIT_MAX       — Max requests per window: 30

# ── Frontend Config ──
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL  — Public API URL for browser requests (e.g., https://myfinpro.example.com/api)
# API_INTERNAL_URL     — Internal API URL for SSR: http://api:3001

# ── Docker Image Config ──
# GHCR_REPO            — GitHub Container Registry repo (lowercase): owner/myfinpro
# IMAGE_TAG            — Docker image tag: latest
